%% E077 - Chat RAG flow sequence - F1-7 API Chat
%% Source: docs/design/f1-7-chat-rag.md (E076), architecture §5, specs 7.2
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Controller as ChatController
    participant MediatR
    participant Validation as ValidationBehavior
    participant Handler as ChatQueryHandler
    participant Embedding as IEmbeddingService
    participant Search as ISearchService
    participant Repo as IRulingRepository
    participant LLM as AzureOpenAiEnrichmentService

    Client->>Controller: POST /api/chat (query)
    Controller->>MediatR: Send(ChatQueryCommand)
    MediatR->>Validation: Validate
    Validation-->>MediatR: ok
    MediatR->>Handler: Handle(ChatQueryCommand)
    Handler->>Embedding: GenerateAsync(query)
    Embedding-->>Handler: embedding vector
    Handler->>Search: SearchChunksAsync(embedding, topK=10)
    Search-->>Handler: chunks (rulingId, text)
    Handler->>Search: SearchRulingsAsync(embedding, topK=5)
    Search-->>Handler: rulings (metadata)
    Handler->>Repo: GetByIdAsync(rulingIds not in results)
    Repo-->>Handler: ruling metadata
    Note over Handler: Build context from chunks + rulings
    Handler->>LLM: StreamChatAsync(system + context + query)
    loop SSE stream
        LLM-->>Handler: chunk
        Handler-->>Controller: chunk
        Controller-->>Client: data: chunk
    end
    LLM-->>Handler: done
    Controller->>Client: stream end
